typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		Year as short,
		City as string,
		Province as string,
		DGUID as string,
		Homicides as short
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> HomicidesCanadaCSV
HomicidesCanadaCSV select(mapColumn(
		Year,
		Province,
		City,
		Homicides
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> DropDGUID
DropDGUID window(over(Year,
		Province),
	desc(Homicides, true),
	RowID = rowNumber()) ~> YearProvince
